# 🇨🇾 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Cyprus Readiness

This folder contains the official readiness brief and rollout strategy for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II expansion into Cyprus.

📄 [Download Cyprus Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Cyprus_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 📌 Key Highlights

- GDPR compliance overseen by the Commissioner for Personal Data Protection – Cyprus
- Participation in EU AI Act initiatives via Ministry of Research & Innovation
- Centralized public health governance through the Ministry of Health
- Multilingual rollout: Greek required; English widely accepted in demos; Turkish optional

---

## 🏛️ Governance & Innovation Partners

- Ministry of Health – Republic of Cyprus
- Office of the Commissioner for Personal Data Protection
- Ministry of Research, Innovation and Digital Policy
- Cyprus University of Technology – Digital Health Research Lab
- Cyprus Institute of Neurology and Genetics

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization

| Language  | Role |
|-----------|------|
| **Greek**    | ✅ Required for public rollout in Republic of Cyprus |
| **English**  | ✅ Widely accepted for pilot demos and innovation use |
| **Turkish**  | 🟡 Optional based on regional pilot needs |

🟢 Demo kits available in Greek and English, with Turkish support upon request.

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload PDF readiness brief
- Begin outreach to Cyprus Ministry of Health and Innovation partners
- Localize Greek-language dashboards and compliance risk monitoring tools
